CouchDB-Simple

A simple interface to CouchDB.

  Usage: couchdb-simple command [arguments]

  Available Commands:
      add   	add a document, content is read from stdin
      delete	delete a document
      get   	get a document
      help  	show syntax and available commands
      update	update a document, content is read from stdin


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc CouchDB::Simple

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=CouchDB-Simple

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/CouchDB-Simple

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/CouchDB-Simple

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/CouchDB-Simple/


